data.content:
Từ điển Đồng nghĩa
fagged
▸ adjective (informal) EXHAUSTED, tired (out), worn out, fatigued, weary, drained, washed out; informal done in, all in, dead beat, dead on one's feet, shattered, bushed; Brit.informal knackered; N. Amer.informal tuckered, pooped.

sentences.vi: Kiệt sức, mệt dốc, mệt lắm

sentences.en: He ran until he was fagged out.
sentences.vi: Anh ta chạy đến khi mệt bở hơi tai.

sentences.en: I was fagged out with that journey.
sentences.vi: Tôi mệt bở hơi tai với chuyến đi đó.

sentences.en: Peter has to work without a break the whole day until he is fagged out.
sentences.vi: Peter phải làm bở hơi tai, suốt cả ngày không nghỉ.
